  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms </strong>are around 32m² and are North facing. These rooms have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Matterhorn Twin Rooms </strong>have balconies and South facing Matterhorn views.</p>
<p><strong>Two Room Suites</strong> are around 63m² and sleep up to three (max two adults and one child). These suites have one twin bedroom and a lounge area with a double sofa bed. They also have balconies with Matterhorn views.</p>
<p><strong>Three Room Suites </strong>are around 95m² and sleep up to four (max two adults and two children OR three adults). These suites have two twin bedrooms and a lounge area with a double sofa bed and balcony with Matterhorn views.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
